Glorified Samba de Amigo rhythm game (no punches here, Vive wands are like maracas) with finally a first class arcade/console quality standard and budget. Things you should know about Airtone:

1) set japanese speech with subtitles in options, so much better!
2) 25 tracks with three different levels each, lot of stuff;
3) challenging, not for those easy to be frustrated;
4) when an item in the room has a rainbow ring, click it for new story details;
5) the main avatar is lovely, high quality cel shading and animation (more details here: http://airtone-vr.com/core_sys/images/contents/00000004/base/l1.jpg );
6) nothing similiar to Audioshield or Soundboxing.
